{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component."}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions","text":"Suggestions","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeCompact"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Version","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"